Package org.concordion.cubano.config

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PropertiesLoader
    Configuration loader interface.
    PropertyLoader
    Loads and lists properties.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CaselessProperties
    A Properties implementation that ignores the case of the properties.
    Config
    Reads and supplies properties from the config.properties file that are required by the framework.
    DefaultPropertiesLoader
    Loads configuration from config.properties and user.properties located in projects root folder.
    DefaultPropertyLoader
    A PropertyLoader which loads a property, firstly checking the userProperties and then the properties.
    ProxyConfig
    Configuration for proxies - used by multiple packages within Cubano.
